*12月16日，据警方的消息，一群武装分子首先使用汽车炸弹袭击了位于[[提克里特|提克里特]]的市议会大楼，然后占领了该建筑，有一名市议员和两名警察在这起事故中丧生。<ref>{{cite news|title=Militants occupy city council in Iraq's Tikrit: police|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-16/241259-militants-occupy-city-council-in-iraqs-tikrit-police.ashx#axzz2lGvTgDRI|accessdate=2013-12-16|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2013-12-16|archive-date=2020-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504220920/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2013/Dec-16/241259-militants-occupy-city-council-in-iraqs-tikrit-police.ashx#axzz2lGvTgDRI|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊拉克安全部队随后包围了该建筑。随后安全部队与武装分子发生了交火，有三名警察和三名武装分子死亡。当天的另一起事件中，枪手杀害了在[[提克里特|提克里特]]石油管道附近站岗的三名士兵。

当天在[[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]的一辆公共汽车上的12人被武装分子杀害。另外，在巴格达，五个汽车炸弹和一个吸附在一辆车上的黏性炸弹爆炸，造成至少17人死亡，超过40人受伤。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/12/16/340306/over-40-died-in-iraq-violence/ | title = More than 40 killed in Iraq bombings, attacks | date = 2013-12-16 | publisher = Press TV | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150627092845/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/12/16/340306/over-40-died-in-iraq-violence/ | archivedate = 2015年6月27日 | accessdate = 2014年6月27日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Militants attack city council as Iraq unrest kills 42|url=http://news.yahoo.com/baghdad-area-bombings-kill-least-nine-081636257.html|accessdate=2013-12-16|newspaper=Yahoo! News|date=2013-12-15|author=Hassan Obeidi, Mahmud Saleh}}</ref>

===2014年===

====1月至6月====

=====安巴爾衝突=====
{{main|安巴爾衝突}}
[[伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯蘭國|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯蘭國]]的民兵於2013年12月30日起於[[安巴爾省|安巴爾省]]爆發軍事衝突。2014年1月初，ISIS更奪取了遜尼派重鎮[[費盧傑|費盧傑]]的控制權。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-25605459 | title=Iraq conflict: Sunni fighters 'control all of Falluja' | publisher=BBC | accessdate=2014-01-04 | archive-date=2020-10-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021083220/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-25605459 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

=====2014年6月伊拉克北部攻勢=====
{{main|2014年伊拉克北部內戰}}
2014年中，内戰演變成更大規模。6月6日，伊斯蘭國於伊拉克北部[[尼尼微省|尼尼微省]]發動[[摩蘇爾陷落|攻擊]]。6月10日，ISIS控制了尼尼微省全境及其首府[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140610_iraq_mosul.shtml | title=激進分子攻佔伊拉克城市摩蘇爾 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-10 | archive-date=2014-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614195248/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140610_iraq_mosul.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>防禦摩蘇爾的政府軍士兵被指於戰爭中拋下自己軍服和武器，並逃離自己的崗位。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-25588623 | title=How can militants take over Iraqi cities? | publisher=BBC | accessdate=2014-06-11 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112025702/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-25588623 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="敘利亞遜尼派武裝越境佔領伊拉克重鎮">{{cite news | url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140611/c11mosul/zh-hant/ | title=敘利亞遜尼派武裝越境佔領伊拉克重鎮 | publisher=紐約時報 | accessdate=2014-06-11 | archive-date=2020-05-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504220953/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140611/c11mosul/zh-hant/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>摩蘇爾約有50萬居民淪為難民，逃往南面的巴格達和東面的[[伊拉克庫德斯坦|伊拉克庫德斯坦]]。<ref name="敘利亞遜尼派武裝越境佔領伊拉克重鎮"/><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140611_iraq_mosul.shtml | title=激摩蘇爾被激進分子佔據 50萬人逃離 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-11}}</ref>不少被俘的政府軍士兵於斯派克營(COB Speicher)遭到IS的處決。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140615_iraq_image.shtmll | title=伊拉克激進武裝公布血腥屠殺照片 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-15 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020218/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140615_iraq_image.shtmll | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=22468 | title=特别代表呼吁对数百名斯派克营被俘者惨遭“伊斯兰国”杀害一事进行公开调查 | publisher=UN | accessdate=2014-09-03 | archive-date=2017-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212193234/http://www.un.org/chinese/News/story.asp?NewsID=22468 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

6月12日，政府軍棄守北部主要油田[[基爾庫克|基爾庫克]]，[[伊拉克庫德斯坦|伊拉克庫爾德族]]武裝部隊順勢接管了當地。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140612_iraq_kurds_kirkuk.shtml | title=伊拉克庫爾德部隊接管石油大城基爾庫克 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-12 | archive-date=2014-06-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615035903/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140612_iraq_kurds_kirkuk.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

11日，[[提克里特|提克里特]]被IS攻下。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140611_islamic_militants_tikrit.shtml | title=伊拉克危機：激進分子攻下提克里克 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-11 | archive-date=2014-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616062516/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140611_islamic_militants_tikrit.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>隨後，IS亦成攻佔北部城市[[泰勒阿費爾|泰勒阿費爾]]，<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140616_iraq_conflict_new.shtml | title=伊拉克危機：遜尼極端武裝又攻陷一城 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-16 | archive-date=2014-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620035902/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140616_iraq_conflict_new.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>並一路南下逼近首都[[巴格達|巴格達]]。政府軍與遜尼派武裝在巴格達郊外的[[巴古拜|巴古拜]]爆發激戰。<ref name="遜尼極端武裝逼近巴格達" />6月18日，ISIS攻入首都巴格達北部210公里處的[[拜伊吉|拜伊吉]]煉油廠。為爭奪此伊拉克最大煉油廠，政府軍與遜尼派武裝爆發激戰。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140618_iraq_baiji.shtml | title=遜尼極端武裝攻入伊拉克最大煉油廠 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-18 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020218/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140618_iraq_baiji.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140620_iraq_fight.shtml | title=伊拉克交戰雙方激戰 爭奪煉油廠和機場 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-20}}</ref>

與此同時在西部，6月21日，IS於黎明前奪取了西部邊境城鎮[[加伊姆|加伊姆]]（Qaim）。伊拉克政府軍撤離當地邊防站。武裝分子因此可以攜帶武器於伊拉克及敘利亞兩國間自由出入，加強了他們向伊拉克中心地帶輸送人員和補給的能力。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/iraq-20140621/1942154.html | title=伊拉克反政府軍奪取伊敘邊境城市 | publisher=美國之音 | accessdate=2014-06-21 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020218/https://www.voachinese.com/a/iraq-20140621/1942154.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140623/c23iraq/| title=遜尼武裝佔領邊境重地，克里暗示樂見伊拉克改選| publisher=紐約時報| accessdate=2014-06-23| archive-date=2020-08-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807113946/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140623/c23iraq/| dead-url=no}}</ref>西部城市[[魯特拜|魯特拜]]亦被攻佔。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140622_iraq_fighting_rutba.shtml | title=伊拉克遜尼派叛軍又下一西部城市 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-22 | archive-date=2014-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029173551/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140622_iraq_fighting_rutba.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>隨後，伊拉克的遜尼派激進武裝又佔領了多兩個邊界關卡。一個關卡在敘利亞邊界，另一個在約旦邊界。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/check-points-taken-iraq/1942645.html | title=伊斯蘭激進武裝佔領更多邊界關卡 | publisher=美國之音 | accessdate=2014-06-27 | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305030529/http://www.voachinese.com/content/check-points-taken-iraq/1942645.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

其後，敘利亞軍機於24日空襲了伊敘邊界加伊姆通道伊拉克一側的目標，並空襲了在伊拉克境內更遠處的西部城市[[魯特拜|魯特拜]]。伊拉克總理[[努里·馬利基|努里·馬利基]]對敘利亞空襲IS武裝目標，表示歡迎。<ref name="敘利亞空襲">{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140626_iraq_syria_strike.shtml | title=馬利基歡迎敘利亞空襲ISIS武裝目標 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-26 | archive-date=2014-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630184336/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140626_iraq_syria_strike.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/syria-iraq-20140626/1945491.html | title=敘利亞伊朗幫助伊拉克抗擊遜尼派反叛武裝 | publisher=美國之音 | date=2014-06-27 | accessdate=2014-06-27 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221546/http://www.voachinese.com/content/syria-iraq-20140626/1945491.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

6月28日，政府軍向北部城市[[提克里特|提克里特]]的遜尼派武裝分子發動了一次反擊。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140628_iraq_army.shtml | title=伊拉克政府軍向提克里特發動反攻 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-28 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912020248/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140628_iraq_army.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>雙方爆發激戰。政府軍直升機對提克里特展開輪番空襲。當日，政府軍遭到頑強抵抗，被迫撤到附近一座小鎮。第二天，政府軍的地面部隊再一次向提克里特推進。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140629_iraq_tikrit.shtml | title=伊拉克：提克里特發生激烈爭奪戰 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-06-29 | archive-date=2014-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707225410/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140629_iraq_tikrit.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

聯合國稱，2014年的叛亂至六月底已造成了超過100萬伊拉克人流離失所。<ref name="百萬伊拉克人流離失所">{{cite news | url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140630/c30iraq/zh-hant/ | title=戰火重燃，百萬伊拉克人流離失所 | publisher=紐約時報 | accessdate=2014-06-30 | archive-date=2020-08-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807125058/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140630/c30iraq/zh-hant/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

===2014年8月===
[[File:President_Obama_Makes_a_Statement_on_Iraq_-_080714.ogv|thumb]]
[[File:FA-18C_Fighter_Iraq_Airstrikes_August_7_2014.JPG|thumb]]上正準備出發的[[F/A-18|F/A-18]]戰鬥機]]
[[File:U.S._FA-18_Super_Hornet_strikes_in_Iraq_August_8_2014.ogv|thumb]]戰鬥機對ISIS展開空襲]]
在8月初時，ISIS在尼尼微省與庫爾德武裝部隊發生激烈交火。最終，庫爾德武裝部隊“自由斗士”先後在祖马尔镇（Zumar）和辛賈爾鎮（Sinjar）被擊潰，被迫撤出當地。聯合國表示，多達200,000名平民在衝突中被迫逃離家園。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140804/c04iraq/zh-hant/| title=遜尼派武裝繼續在伊拉克北部擴張| publisher=紐約時報 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-04| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221123/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140804/c04iraq/zh-hant/| dead-url=no}}</ref>辛賈爾鎮當地[[雅茲迪教派|雅茲迪教派]]的兩個聖地已經被ISIS搗毀。祖马尔鎮兩個附近的油田亦落入ISIS手中，這使他們的軍事行動有了更多的資金來源。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140803_islam_state_iraq.shtml | title=伊斯蘭國武裝攻城略地引起聯合國擔憂 | publisher=BBC中文網 | accessdate=2014-08-03 | archive-date=2014-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029005926/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140803_islam_state_iraq.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>在庫爾德部隊撤離後，ISIS也控制了[[摩蘇爾水壩|摩蘇爾水壩]]。摩蘇爾水壩是伊拉克最大的水壩，為摩蘇爾提供大部份的電力。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28631770 | title=UN warns of 'tragedy' as militants take over Iraq towns | publisher=BBC NEWS | accessdate=2014-08-03 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013157/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28631770 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在庫爾德人武裝8月6日撤離尼尼微省的克拉克斯（Qaraqosh）後，ISIS一夜間佔領了該市。克拉克斯是伊拉克基督教社區最大的城鎮，有多至四分之一的居民為基督教徒。過萬名伊拉克基督教徒已逃離家園，到庫德斯坦自治區避難。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28686998 | title=Iraq Christians flee as Islamic State takes Qaraqosh | publisher=BBC NEWS | accessdate=2014-08-07 | archive-date=2021-01-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117020059/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28686998 | dead-url=no }}</ref>與此同時，在辛賈爾鎮淪陷後，4萬名[[雅茲迪教派|雅茲迪教派]]教徒被困辛賈爾山，缺乏食物和水等資源。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28687329 | title=Eyewitness describes plight of Iraq's trapped Yazidis | publisher=BBC NEWS | accessdate=2014-08-07 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013749/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28687329 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140807/41483052_0.shtml| title=4万伊拉克人被ISIS困在深山：要么渴死 要么被杀| publisher=凤凰网| accessdate=2014-08-07| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221145/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140807/41483052_0.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

美國警告說，伊拉克境內的少數民族境況正變成「人道災難」。8月7日，美國總統奧巴馬表示，他已授權對伊拉克北部的伊斯蘭極端武裝ISIS目標實施定點空襲，及對受到伊斯蘭極端武裝ISIS威脅的伊拉克地區提供人道援助的空投。奧巴馬表示，美國的空襲將瞄凖伊斯蘭極端武裝ISIS士兵，他們一旦向[[埃爾比勒|埃爾比勒]]進發，就將遭到空襲。<ref name="奧巴馬授權美國空襲伊拉克極端武裝">{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140807_obama_us_air-strikes_iraq.shtml| title=奧巴馬授權美國空襲伊拉克極端武裝| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-08| archive-date=2014-11-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120040758/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140807_obama_us_air-strikes_iraq.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月8日，美國五角大樓稱，美軍已經開始對伊拉克北部的ISIS目標實施空襲。兩架美國[[F/A-18|F/A-18]]戰鬥機已經在[[埃爾比勒|埃爾比勒]]附近進行首輪空襲，對ISIS的火炮和拖帶其的卡車投下500磅的激光制導炸彈。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28709530 | title=Iraq: US air strike on Islamic State militants in Iraq | publisher=BBC NEWS | accessdate=2014-08-08 | archive-date=2020-12-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217005239/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28709530 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/09/world/middleeast/iraq.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&version=BannerSubHedSumLargeMedia&module=a-lede-package-region&region=lede-package&WT.nav=lede-package | title=U.S. Begins Strikes in Iraq, Pentagon Says | publisher=New York Times | accessdate=2014-08-08 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111201942/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/09/world/middleeast/iraq.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&version=BannerSubHedSumLargeMedia&module=a-lede-package-region&region=lede-package&WT.nav=lede-package | dead-url=no }}</ref>同日，美軍再對ISIS又發動了兩次空襲。出動了無人駕駛飛機及F/A-18戰鬥機，分別擊中了ISIS的迫擊炮陣地及車隊。<ref name="U.S. Jets and Drones Attack Militants in Iraq, Hoping to Stop Advance" /><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140808_iraq_us.shtml| title=美國加緊空襲伊拉克北部伊斯蘭激進分子| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-08| archive-date=2014-11-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141127132058/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140808_iraq_us.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>並且以三架軍機總共向伊拉克難民空投了72包人道主義物資，共3.6萬個餐盒與3萬公升飲用水。<ref name="美國空襲伊激進武裝並完成二次人道空投">{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140809_iraq-conflict_us_aid_drop.shtml| title=美國空襲伊激進武裝並完成二次人道空投| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-08| archive-date=2014-11-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141127132549/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140809_iraq-conflict_us_aid_drop.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

次日，美軍再進行了新一輪的四次空襲行動，以戰鬥機和無人機摧毀了包圍辛賈爾山的一批ISIS的[[裝甲運兵車|裝甲運兵車]]和卡車。<ref name="奧巴馬稱空襲ISIS行動或持續數月">{{cite news| url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140810/c10iraq/zh-hant/| title=美奧巴馬稱空襲ISIS行動或持續數月| publisher=紐約時報 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-10| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221220/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140810/c10iraq/zh-hant/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140809_us_new_airstrike.shtml| title=美軍對伊北部武裝展開新一輪定點空襲| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-09| archive-date=2014-08-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813102726/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140809_us_new_airstrike.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月10日，首批的英國人道主義物資被空投至辛賈爾山的難民。<ref name="first UK aid dropped in Iraq for Yazidis who fled IS militants">{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-28730743| title=First UK aid dropped in Iraq for Yazidis who fled IS militants| publisher=BBC News| accessdate=2014-08-10| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221224/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-28730743| dead-url=no}}</ref>美軍在埃爾比勒再進行了五輪的空襲行動<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.defensenews.com/article/20140810/DEFREG04/308100009/US-Confirms-Fresh-Airstrikes-Against-Militants-Near-Arbil| title=US Confirms Fresh Airstrikes Against Militants Near Arbil| publisher=defensenews| accessdate=2014-08-10| archive-date=2014-08-11| archive-url=https://archive.today/20140811173636/http://www.defensenews.com/article/20140810/DEFREG04/308100009/US-Confirms-Fresh-Airstrikes-Against-Militants-Near-Arbil| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/11/us-iraq-security-usa-strikes-idUSKBN0GA0NT20140811| title=U.S. strikes Islamic State targets near Iraqi Kurdish capital Arbil| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-10| archive-date=2015-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203404/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/11/us-iraq-security-usa-strikes-idUSKBN0GA0NT20140811| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在美軍支援下庫爾德武裝部隊亦順勢展開反攻，奪回埃爾比勒附近兩個小鎮——馬克穆爾（Makhmur）與葛沃（Gwer）。<ref name="伊拉克庫爾德人反攻遜尼派武裝">{{cite news| url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140811/c11iraq/zh-hant/| title=伊拉克庫爾德人反攻遜尼派武裝| publisher=紐約時報中文網| accessdate=2014-08-11| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221245/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140811/c11iraq/zh-hant/| dead-url=no}}</ref>

在過去三天，在美國的空襲行動和庫爾德部隊幫助下，數千名雅茲迪人逃脫包圍，步行穿過敘利亞領土來到庫爾德人控制下的伊拉克邊境城鎮費希哈布爾(Fishkhabour)，但仍有過數千名雅茲迪人被困在山上。<ref name="伊拉克庫爾德人反攻遜尼派武裝" /><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/11/us-iraq-security-un-idUSKBN0GB20V20140811| title=Kurdish forces and others aiding escape from Iraqi mountain: U.N.| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-11| archive-date=2015-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203402/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/11/us-iraq-security-un-idUSKBN0GB20V20140811| dead-url=yes}}</ref>8月12日，大約十幾名[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]和特種作戰部隊士兵抵達伊拉克北部的山區，並在那裡待了24小時，以評估難民的狀況。美國國防部根據他們的回報表示，辛賈爾山被圍困平民的人道狀況已經得到了很大的改善，仍然被困的難民比預期要少，許多雅茲迪人已經逃離了辛賈爾山。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140814/c14refugee/zh-hant/| title=美軍行動助伊拉克北部難民解困| publisher=紐約時報中文網| accessdate=2014-08-14| archive-date=2020-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221253/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20140814/c14refugee/zh-hant/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140814_iraq-crisis_us_sinjar.shtml| title=美國稱未必展開伊拉克山區難民疏散行動| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-14| archive-date=2014-08-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821022213/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140814_iraq-crisis_us_sinjar.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140814_obama_iraq.shtmll| title=奧巴馬稱伊拉克被困平民的人道狀況改善| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-14}}</ref>

8月15日，庫爾德官員表示ISIS武裝分子在離辛賈爾山約45公里外的庫奇奧村莊，屠殺了80名拒絕皈依伊斯蘭教的雅茲迪人。<ref name="伊拉克危機：雅茲迪教村民「遭屠殺」">{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140816_iraq-crisis_yazidi_villagers.shtml| title=伊拉克危機：雅茲迪教村民「遭屠殺」| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-16| archive-date=2014-08-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820233340/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140816_iraq-crisis_yazidi_villagers.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/16/us-iraq-security-yazidis-killings-idUSKBN0GG0AJ20140816| title=Islamic State 'massacres' 80 Yazidis in north Iraq: officials| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-16| archive-date=2015-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203525/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/16/us-iraq-security-yazidis-killings-idUSKBN0GG0AJ20140816| dead-url=yes}}</ref>美國軍方表示，在接收到來自庫爾德勢力的報告後，便出動兩架無人飛機，在辛賈爾山附近襲擊並摧毀了被認為屬於「伊斯蘭國」武裝分子的兩輛汽車。<ref name="伊拉克危機：雅茲迪教村民「遭屠殺」" /><ref>{{cite web| title =Aug. 15: U.S. Military Conducts Airstrikes Against ISIL Near Sinjar| publisher =U.S. Central Command| url =http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-15-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-sinjar| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140818200921/http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-15-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-sinjar| archivedate =2014-08-18| accessdate =2014-08-17}}</ref>

8月16日，美軍戰鬥機及無人機在摩蘇爾水壩附近展開空襲。九次的空襲中共摧毀或損壞4輛[[裝甲運兵車|裝甲運兵車]](APC)，七輛武裝卡車，兩輛[[悍馬_(軍用汽車)|悍馬車]]和一輛[[裝甲車|裝甲車]]。<ref>{{cite web| title = U.S. Military Conducts Airstrikes Against ISIL Near Irbil, the Mosul Dam| publisher = U.S. Central Command| url = http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/us-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-irbil-the-mosul-dam| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140819130107/http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/us-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-irbil-the-mosul-dam| archivedate = 2014-08-19| accessdate = 2014-08-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/16/us-iraq-security-usa-strikes-idUSKBN0GG0KQ20140816| title=U.S. says conducts air strikes in Iraq near Arbil and Mosul dam| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-16| archive-date=2015-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203523/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/16/us-iraq-security-usa-strikes-idUSKBN0GG0KQ20140816| dead-url=yes}}</ref>在美軍戰鬥機支援下，伊拉克庫爾德部隊向[[摩蘇爾大壩|摩蘇爾大壩]]附近ISIS陣地發動反攻。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140816_us_iraq_bombing_is.shtml| title=伊拉克危機：美軍機助庫族部隊爭奪大壩| publisher=BBC 中文網| accessdate=2014-08-16| archive-date=2014-08-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819010915/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/08/140816_us_iraq_bombing_is.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月17日，美軍繼續在摩蘇爾水壩附近展開空襲ISIL恐怖分子，空襲摧毀了ISIS三架武裝車輛，一個架車載[[防空砲|防空砲]]及一個檢查站。<ref>{{cite web| title = Aug. 17: U.S. Military Conducts Airstrikes Against ISIL Near the Mosul Dam| publisher = U.S. Central Command| url = http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-17-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-the-mosul-dam2| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140818094707/http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-17-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-the-mosul-dam2| archivedate = 2014-08-18| accessdate = 2014-08-18}}</ref>8月18日，美軍加強空襲力度，以戰鬥機、[[轟炸機|轟炸機]]以及無人機在摩蘇爾水壩附近展開一共15次的空襲。摧毀了ISIS九個[[散兵坑|散兵坑]]、 一個檢查點、 6 架武裝車輛、一架輕型裝甲車輛及一台車載防空火砲。自8月8日起至18日為止，[[美國中央司令部|美國中央司令部]]已經進行了共68次空襲。68次空襲中有35次是用以支援摩蘇爾水壩附近的庫爾德部隊。<ref>{{cite web| title = Aug. 18: U.S. Military Conducts Airstrikes Against ISIL near the Mosul Dam| publisher = U.S. Central Command| url = http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-18-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-the-mosul-dam| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140819082534/http://www.centcom.mil/en/news/articles/aug.-18-u.s.-military-conducts-airstrikes-against-isil-near-the-mosul-dam| archivedate = 2014-08-19| accessdate = 2014-08-18}}</ref>

8月18日，庫爾德人在美軍支援下，成功奪退ISIS武裝分子，並重新奪回摩蘇爾水壩。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/18/us-iraq-security-idUSKBN0GH0JL20140818| title=Backed by U.S. strikes, Iraq Kurds retake strategic dam: officials| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-18| archive-date=2015-09-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924203538/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/18/us-iraq-security-idUSKBN0GH0JL20140818| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.reuters.com/video/2014/08/18/obama-confirms-us-helped-iraqi-kurdish-f?videoId=340525157| title=Obama confirms U.S. helped Iraqi, Kurdish forces retake dam| publisher=Reuters| accessdate=2014-08-18| archive-date=2019-05-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515022555/https://www.reuters.com/video/2014/08/18/obama-confirms-us-helped-iraqi-kurdish-f?videoId=340525157| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28858601| title=Iraq crisis: Mosul dam 'back in safe hands'| publisher=BBC News| accessdate=2014-08-19| archive-date=2016-08-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823235247/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28858601| dead-url=no}}</ref>

