11月18日，伊拉克安全部队在巴格达西部一个[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]武器储藏处起获大量武器。包括500公斤爆炸物、轻型和中型武器、伊斯兰国黑色旗帜、通信设备和[[简易爆炸装置|简易爆炸装置]]。这些武器是美国以空袭为掩饰通过空投提供给伊斯兰国武装分子的。起获的武器中包括价值不菲的可穿透装甲车的子弹。而通常這些武器是只能由美国提供给与[[五角大楼|五角大楼]]合作的伙伴。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/573188/20141118/u-s-arms-isis-iraqi-intel-weapons.htm |language=en |title=U.S. Arms The ISIS - Iraqi Intel |publisher=International Business Times |date=2014-11-18 |accessdate=2016-10-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221131802/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/573188/20141118/u-s-arms-isis-iraqi-intel-weapons.htm |archivedate=2014-12-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.globalresearch.ca/isis-made-in-usa-iraq-geopolitical-arsonists-seek-to-burn-region/5387475 |language=en |script-title=en:ISIS “Made in USA”. Iraq “Geopolitical Arsonists” Seek to Burn Region |publisher=GlobalResearch |date=2014-06-18 |accessdate=2014-12-10 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116045324/https://www.globalresearch.ca/isis-made-in-usa-iraq-geopolitical-arsonists-seek-to-burn-region/5387475 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

11月20日，伊拉克安全部队与库尔德武装份子在什叶派民兵的支援下经过和[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]两天激战重新控制了在首都[[巴格达|巴格达]]东北方约120公里的萨阿迪耶市。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20141121/42536635_0.shtml|title=伊拉克政府军夺回东部城镇 武装冲突继续进行|publisher=凤凰网|date=2014年11月21日|accessdate=2014年11月23日|archive-date=2020年5月4日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504090656/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20141121/42536635_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日，有消息指[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]在[[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]的负责人拉德旺·塔勒布·哈姆多尼和他的司机在[[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]遭遇空袭身亡，不过美方则无法确定哈姆多尼是否已经死亡。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/20/radwan-taleb-al-hamdouni_n_6191500.html|title=Radwan Taleb Al-Hamdouni Dead: Senior Islamic State Figure Reportedly Killed In Mosul|publisher=The Huffington Post|date=2014-11-20|accessdate=2014-11-23|archive-date=2016-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160831153041/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/20/radwan-taleb-al-hamdouni_n_6191500.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

11月23日，伊拉克安全部队、库尔德武装与什叶派民兵重新控制了{{tsl|en|Jalawla|贾劳拉}}和萨阿迪耶两个城镇 <ref>{{cite news |url=http://mobile.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN0J70AX20141123?irpc=932 |title=Iraqi forces say retake two towns from Islamic State |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-11-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192718/http://mobile.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN0J70AX20141123?irpc=932 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

12月21日，庫爾德武裝和雅茲迪戰士在美國空襲支持下，橫掃辛賈爾山北側，成功打破伊斯蘭國對辛賈爾山五個月來的圍攻。並且向[[辛賈爾鎮|辛賈爾鎮]]挺進，嘗試奪回失地。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30569313 |title=Sinjar battle: Kurds 'take control' of large area from IS |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2014-12-21 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202215126/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30569313 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/21/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-sinjar-idUSKBN0JZ0QO20141221 |title=Iraqi Kurds, Yazidis fight Islamic State for strategic town of Sinjar |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-12-21 |archive-date=2015-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128104841/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/21/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-sinjar-idUSKBN0JZ0QO20141221 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===2015年1月至2月===
2月12日，伊斯蘭國經數月的圍攻後，成功攻入位於[[安巴爾省|安巴爾省]]的巴格達迪鎮，並威脅到類近的{{en-link|阿薩德空軍基地|al-Asad air base}}。該基地內駐守了約320位正在訓練伊拉克第7師的[[美國海軍陸戰隊|美國海軍陸戰隊]]成員。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/13/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-anbar-idUSKBN0LG23120150213 |title=Islamic State fighters seize parts of western Iraqi town: officials |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-02-12 |archive-date=2015-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120062403/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/13/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-anbar-idUSKBN0LG23120150213 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2月13日，約20至25伊斯蘭國武裝分子對阿薩德空軍基地進行襲擊。伊拉克安全部隊成功擊退了伊斯蘭國對基地的攻擊。沒有伊拉克或美軍士兵被打死或打傷。美軍亦沒有參與槍戰。美國無人駕駛偵察機和阿帕奇攻擊直升機曾由巴格達飛往現場，但是次襲擊在他們到達前已結束，所以並沒有從事戰鬥。但基地附近的巴格達迪鎮，衝突還在持繼。美國軍於12和13日於發動了五次空襲是在阿薩德基地東部約15公里。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/13/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-anbar-idUSKBN0LH1JD20150213 |title=Iraqi army repels attack on base hosting U.S. Marines: officials |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-02-13 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925122013/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/13/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-anbar-idUSKBN0LH1JD20150213 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_ISLAMIC_STATE_AIR_BASE_ATTACK?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT |title=US: ISLAMIC STATE FIGHTERS KILLED BY IRAQI FORCES |publisher=Associated Press |accessdate=2014-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214071208/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_ISLAMIC_STATE_AIR_BASE_ATTACK?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT |archivedate=2015-02-14 }}</ref>3月初，伊拉克軍隊將IS武裝從巴格達迪趕走。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/03/150307_is-crisis_iraq_army_key-town| title=伊拉克軍隊從西部重鎮趕走IS武裝|publisher=BBC NNEWS |accessdate=2014-03-07}}</ref>

===2015年3月 第二次提克里特戰役===
3月2日，伊拉克政府軍和伊朗支持的什葉派民兵向[[薩拉丁省|薩拉丁省]]發動[[第二次提克里特之戰|反攻]]。在伊拉克空軍支援之下，2萬至3萬名伊拉克士兵和民兵從[[薩邁拉|薩邁拉]]向北前進，往[[提克里特|提克里特]]挺進。這次進攻是全省自去年六月以來最大的軍事行動。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/02/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0LX1QL20150302 |title=Iraq launches attack to retake Tikrit from Islamic State |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2015-03-02 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929062235/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/02/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0LX1QL20150302 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/03/150302_iraq_is_tikrit_mosul|title=伊拉克發動攻擊從「伊斯蘭國」奪回失地|publisher=BBC NNEWS|accessdate=2015-03-02|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311050539/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/03/150302_iraq_is_tikrit_mosul|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月8日，伊拉克政府軍逼近提克里特，並攻下提克里特市南部郊區一個名為al-Dour的小鎮<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/08/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M40LZ20150308 |title=Iraqi troops, militia make advances near Tikrit |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001063132/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/08/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M40LZ20150308 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並向提克里特北面Al-Alam鎮進攻以實現對提克里特市進行南北夾擊。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/08/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M30S720150308 |title=Iraqi troops battle to advance in towns on edge of Tikrit |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929195205/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/08/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M30S720150308 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

3月11日，政府軍收復Al-Alam，並且攻入提克里特北區。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/11/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M60UD20150311 |title=Iraqi troops, militia retake strategic town north of Tikrit from Islamic State |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929220417/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/11/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0M60UD20150311 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201503110439-1.aspx|title=反攻伊斯蘭國 伊軍挺進提克里特|publisher=中央社|accessdate=2015-03-11|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817080235/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201503110439-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

為了讓伊拉克部隊的推進速度放慢，伊斯蘭國武裝份子將整個提克里特地區唯一橫跨[[底格里斯河|底格里斯河]]的橋梁炸毀。該橋梁是由東方通住提克里特的唯一通道。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/search/hydetailws.aspx?qid=201503110006&q=%E6%8F%90%E5%85%8B%E9%87%8C%E7%89%B9|title=伊拉克部隊逼近 伊斯蘭國炸提克里特橋|publisher=中央社|accessdate=2014-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403194603/http://www.cna.com.tw/search/hydetailws.aspx?qid=201503110006|archive-date=2015-04-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>武裝份子在市內部處狙擊手和[[IED|IED]]炸彈，使政府軍攻勢停滯不前。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/13/us-mideast-iraq-idUSKBN0M91DR20150313 |title=Iraqi forces pause in battle to drive Islamic State from Tikrit |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2015-03-13 |archive-date=2015-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928224900/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/13/us-mideast-iraq-idUSKBN0M91DR20150313 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

3月25日，由於戰局進入膠着狀態，美國戰機開始對提克里特的伊斯蘭國陣地發起空襲。伊拉克官員對空襲表示歡迎。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150326/c26iraq/zh-hant/|title=美軍轉變角色，轟炸巴格達北部ISIS武裝|publisher=紐約時報|accessdate=2015-03-26|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715010302/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150326/c26iraq/zh-hant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但此舉卻引起由伊朗人領導的什葉派民兵的抵制，有三個民兵團體撤出提克里特的戰場以示不滿。
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150327/c27iraq/zh-hant/|title=美國空襲ISIS遭什葉派民兵抵制|publisher=紐約時報|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715010219/https://cn.nytimes.com/world/20150327/c27iraq/zh-hant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月31日，原本退出戰鬥的什葉派民兵在在總理阿巴迪的請求下又重回戰場。同時，伊拉克政府軍攻入提克里特市中心，並宣佈成功解放提克里特。薩拉赫丁省政府總部和提克里特醫院都回到政府軍手中。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/01/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-tikrit-idUSKBN0MR1G420150401 |title=Iraqi forces drive Islamic State out of central Tikrit: PM |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-04-01 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001015921/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/01/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-tikrit-idUSKBN0MR1G420150401 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/04/01/world/middleeast/ap-ml-islamic-state.html?_r=0|title=Iraq Hails Victory Over Islamic State Extremists in Tikrit|publisher=New York Times|accessdate=2015-04-01|archive-date=2015-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150419211601/http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/04/01/world/middleeast/ap-ml-islamic-state.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2015年4月===
自[[提克里特|提克里特]]失守後，IS向[[安巴爾省|安巴爾省]]的首府[[拉馬迪|拉馬迪]]及[[拜伊吉|拜伊吉市]]發動反攻。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/15/us-usa-iraq-abadi-idUSKBN0N62RL20150415 |title=Iraq says Islamic State still fierce; eyes Baiji, Anbar fights |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-04-15 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002092210/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/15/us-usa-iraq-abadi-idUSKBN0N62RL20150415 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>4月18日,伊拉克軍隊將IS再度趕出拜伊吉。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/18/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-refinery-idUSKBN0N90F320150418 |title=Iraqi forces retake most of Baiji refinery from Islamic State |publisher=the Reuters |accessdate=2014-04-18 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002205958/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/18/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-refinery-idUSKBN0N90F320150418 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

