12月初，政府軍北部和西部戰線取得進展，奪回了北部的Albu Farraj和Albu Ziyab，以及西部的Tamim區。政府軍又在幼發拉底河上建造浮橋，準備攻入市中心。<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi forces dislodge Islamic State militants from two key areas in Ramadi|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0TT23Z20151211|publisher=Reuters|date=2015-12-10|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221847/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0TT23Z20151211|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=IS conflict: Iraqi forces 'retake key Ramadi district'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35038983|publisher=Reuters|date=2015-12-08|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128043823/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35038983|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月22日，伊拉克安全部隊向對拉馬迪市中心發起進攻。他們經過浮橋，自北面和西面進入拉馬迪市中心，並向政府大樓推進。<ref>{{cite news|title=Islamic State conflict: Iraqi forces push into Ramadi|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35165747|publisher=BBC|date=2015-12-23|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142313/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35165747|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月28日，政府軍攻下拉馬迪政府大樓，並升起伊拉克國旗。<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi forces raise flag above government complex in Ramadi|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0UB0TW20151228|publisher=Reuters|date=2015-12-238|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142953/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0UB0TW20151228|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=伊拉克軍隊聲稱已奪回拉馬迪政府辦公樓|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/12/151227_iraq_ramadi|publisher=BBC|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221907/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/12/151227_iraq_ramadi|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊拉克政府宣布完成自伊斯蘭國手中解放拉馬迪市。<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraq declares Ramadi liberated from Islamic State|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35188479|publisher=BBC|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131008/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35188479|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi army declares first major victory over Islamic State in Ramadi|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0UA0DH20151228|publisher=Reuters|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2015-12-28|archive-date=2020-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504221919/https://www.reuters.com/article/mideast-crisis-iraq-ramadi-idUSKBN0UA0DH20151228|dead-url=no}}</ref>

